Package: ClimateTrend
Title: Climate Trend Analysis and ETCCDI Toolkit
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Hemal", "Mewantha", email = "mewanmuna2000@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A high-performance toolkit for processing NetCDF climate data, calculating spatial ETCCDI precipitation and drought indices (like SPI, CDD, R95p), and performing parallelized Mann-Kendall trend analysis. Features automated spatial masking for administrative boundaries and river basins.
